ld/meet-antoine-moses-canadian-tree-lover-sets-a-second-guinness-world-record-by-planting-47460-trees-in-just-24-hours-on-the-kenyan-coast/articleshow/131381844.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-29T09:59:58+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131381909,imgsize-71178.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[A 2,000-year-old stone found in Karnak temple reveals a Roman emperor hidden in the form of an Egyptian pharaoh]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131381493.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-2000-year-old-stone-found-in-karnak-temple-reveals-a-roman-emperor-hidden-in-the-form-of-an-egyptian-pharaoh/articleshow/131381493.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-2000-year-old-stone-found-in-karnak-temple-reveals-a-roman-emperor-hidden-in-the-form-of-an-egyptian-pharaoh/articleshow/131381493.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-29T09:34:14+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131381503,imgsize-112348.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Italy on red alert as France, Portugal beat hottest May day record]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131380258.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Italy issued a red alert warning for the capital Rome on Thursday and Portugal and France reported their hottest days in May as Europe struggled with a heatwave that has smashed records across the continent. Britain and France have already reported their hottest-ever May days this week as a "heat dome" brought sweltering temperatures usually unseen until high summer to western Europe.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/italy-on-red-alert-as-france-portugal-beat-hottest-may-day-record/articleshow/131380258.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/italy-on-red-alert-as-france-portugal-beat-hottest-may-day-record/articleshow/131380258.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-29T07:51:47+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131380278,imgsize-1047963.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Why ‘Looksmaxxing’ streamer Androgenic got kicked off a Jetstar flight despite claiming medical clearance?]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131379678.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Ronan Androgenic, a Brisbane-based “looksmaxxing” streamer, was removed from a Jetstar flight after staff said he appeared too unwell to travel following facial surgery in Thailand. Androgenic argued he was simply tired and had medical clearance. Jetstar later said crew members can refuse boarding if they believe a passenger is not fit to fly safely.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-looksmaxxing-streamer-androgenic-got-kicked-off-a-jetstar-flight-despite-claiming-medical-clearance/articleshow/131379678.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-looksmaxxing-streamer-androgenic-got-kicked-off-a-jetstar-flight-despite-claiming-medical-clearance/articleshow/131379678.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-29T06:10:31+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131379674,imgsize-851564.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["I'm done with the abuse": QTCinderella threatens legal action against “hate farming” clip accounts after emotional return online]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131379511.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Popular Twitch streamer QTCinderella has announced plans to take legal action against clip accounts that allegedly use her stream content to spread harassment and misleading narratives. Returning online after grieving the loss of her dog Swift, she said she would issue DMCA takedowns against malicious reposts. The move comes amid growing concerns over “clip farming” on social media, where creators’ content is repackaged with misleading context to generate engagement and fuel online hate campaigns.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/im-done-with-the-abuse-qtcinderella-threatens-legal-action-against-hate-farming-clip-accounts-after-emotional-return-online/articleshow/131379511.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/im-done-with-the-abuse-qtcinderella-threatens-legal-action-against-hate-farming-clip-accounts-after-emotional-return-online/articleshow/131379511.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-29T05:52:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131379511,imgsize-80148.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Attacking Erika IS attacking Charlie": Candace Owens drags Charlie Kirk’s old support into escalating online firestorm]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131379499.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A resurfaced video of Charlie Kirk defending Candace Owens has reignited debate online. In the clip, Kirk calls Owens “the best” and says, “We're on Team Candace.” Owens shared the video, writing that Kirk “always had my back.” However, many social media users criticized her, arguing that her recent attacks on Kirk’s family and organization contradict the loyalty and support he once showed her.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/attacking-erika-is-attacking-charlie-candace-owens-drags-charlie-kirks-old-support-into-escalating-online-firestorm/articleshow/131379499.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/attacking-erika-is-attacking-charlie-candace-owens-drags-charlie-kirks-old-support-into-escalating-online-firestorm/articleshow/131379499.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-29T05:31:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131379499,imgsize-42026.cms"/></item></channel></rss>